             was indicted for <rs id="t18090920-24-off134" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090920-24-off134" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090920-24-off134" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18090920-24-cd135" type="crimeDate">15th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090920-24-off134 t18090920-24-cd135"></join>, 17 ounces weight of tobacco, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18090920-24-victim229" type="victimName">
                     Proctor 
